  "difficultyLevel": 5,
  "lyrics": "Oh, oh, you know Oh, oh, oh, you know Just how to touch me the right way Just how to make my mind go crazy Baby, you touch me right in my sweet spot Now I don't know what to do with this I don't know how to do this memory Should I let it go Or remember the glimpse of beauty I got last night Baby, I know you don't wanna show me your sweet spot But I sorta like the way you came on to me Drunk a little bit, now you can't find the words to tell me That you're in love with me, baby But if you find, you might just Huh, let me get inside and touch the sweet Youth inside of all of you I can feel a little bit of that falling all over my fingers And we're flying away Beyond the hurl of your memory And my inability to take your face without your heel Baby, be with me more I just want you to know All I see and all I adore Is all in your sweetness, baby Come on, come on, give me some of that Sweet inside, soft side I don't care if you wanna run and hide I'll find the you that you want So that the world can see What you're really made of, baby Come and find that sweet with me And I'll see no you down in the village Wanna know if your name is really your name Or you pretend this is mad for real Or are you looking for real? Cause if you look down next to you You're gonna find me waiting on the things That you said you would be Waiting on the things that you swore were sweet Like the candy I know you are sweet Like the woman I know you came from, baby Can't you make her look that way when you look at me? Sweet Like a candy dot in the morning Do you have me in your love? Oh, then Tell Pummy how sweet frosting all over me, baby Treat you",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 7.480000019073486,
      "text": "Oh, oh, you know",
      "start": 0
    },
    {
      "end": 14.399999618530273,
      "text": "Oh, oh, oh, you know",
      "start": 8.9399995803833
    },
    {
      "end": 17,
      "text": "Just how to touch me the right way",
      "start": 14.399999618530273
    },
    {
      "end": 21.100000381469727,
      "text": "Just how to make my mind go crazy",
      "start": 17.600000381469727
    },
    {
      "end": 28.719999313354492,
      "text": "Baby, you touch me right in my sweet spot",
      "start": 21.739999771118164
    },
    {
      "end": 32.02000045776367,
      "text": "Now I don't know what to do with this",
      "start": 28.719999313354492
    },
    {
      "end": 35.08000183105469,
      "text": "I don't know how to do this memory",
      "start": 32.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 37.13999938964844,
      "text": "Should I let it go",
      "start": 35.08000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 41.63999938964844,
      "text": "Or remember the glimpse of beauty I got last night",
      "start": 37.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 47.380001068115234,
      "text": "Baby, I know you don't wanna show me your sweet spot",
      "start": 42.58000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 51.81999969482422,
      "text": "But I sorta like the way you came on to me",
      "start": 47.380001068115234
    },
    {
      "end": 58.47999954223633,
      "text": "Drunk a little bit, now you can't find the words to tell me",
      "start": 51.84000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 61.779998779296875,
      "text": "That you're in love with me, baby",
      "start": 58.47999954223633
    },
    {
      "end": 66.66000366210938,
      "text": "But if you find, you might just",
      "start": 61.779998779296875
    },
    {
      "end": 71.22000122070312,
      "text": "Huh, let me get inside and touch the sweet",
      "start": 66.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 76.95999908447266,
      "text": "Youth inside of all of you",
      "start": 73.26000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 82.33999633789062,
      "text": "I can feel a little bit of that falling all over my fingers",
      "start": 76.95999908447266
    },
    {
      "end": 87.13999938964844,
      "text": "And we're flying away",
      "start": 82.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 93.95999908447266,
      "text": "Beyond the hurl of your memory",
      "start": 89.12000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 98.19999694824219,
      "text": "And my inability to take your face without your heel",
      "start": 93.95999908447266
    },
    {
      "end": 99.86000061035156,
      "text": "Baby, be with me more",
      "start": 98.19999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 103.58000183105469,
      "text": "I just want you to know",
      "start": 100.19999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 107.9800033569336,
      "text": "All I see and all I adore",
      "start": 104.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 111.0999984741211,
      "text": "Is all in your sweetness, baby",
      "start": 108.19999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 115.4800033569336,
      "text": "Come on, come on, give me some of that",
      "start": 112.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 118.76000213623047,
      "text": "Sweet inside, soft side",
      "start": 115.4800033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 122.08000183105469,
      "text": "I don't care if you wanna run and hide",
      "start": 118.76000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 125.5199966430664,
      "text": "I'll find the you that you want",
      "start": 122.08000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 129.0399932861328,
      "text": "So that the world can see",
      "start": 125.5199966430664
    },
    {
      "end": 133.5800018310547,
      "text": "What you're really made of, baby",
      "start": 129.0399932861328
    },
    {
      "end": 137.6999969482422,
      "text": "Come and find that sweet with me",
      "start": 134.5
    },
    {
      "end": 141.55999755859375,
      "text": "And I'll see no you down in the village",
      "start": 137.6999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 145.05999755859375,
      "text": "Wanna know if your name is really your name",
      "start": 141.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 148.39999389648438,
      "text": "Or you pretend this is mad for real",
      "start": 145.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 151.97999572753906,
      "text": "Or are you looking for real?",
      "start": 148.83999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 157.10000610351562,
      "text": "Cause if you look down next to you",
      "start": 153.97999572753906
    },
    {
      "end": 159.89999389648438,
      "text": "You're gonna find me waiting on the things",
      "start": 157.10000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 161.97999572753906,
      "text": "That you said you would be",
      "start": 159.89999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 166.02000427246094,
      "text": "Waiting on the things that you swore were sweet",
      "start": 161.97999572753906
    },
    {
      "end": 169.86000061035156,
      "text": "Like the candy I know you are sweet",
      "start": 166.3000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 174.0800018310547,
      "text": "Like the woman I know you came from, baby",
      "start": 169.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 179.32000732421875,
      "text": "Can't you make her look that way when you look at me?",
      "start": 174.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 181.6999969482422,
      "text": "Sweet",
      "start": 180.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 185.47999572753906,
      "text": "Like a candy dot in the morning",
      "start": 182.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 187.77999877929688,
      "text": "Do you have me in your love?",
      "start": 185.47999572753906
    },
    {
      "end": 191.05999755859375,
      "text": "Oh, then",
      "start": 189.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 196.10000610351562,
      "text": "Tell Pummy how sweet frosting all over me, baby",
      "start": 191.3800048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 201.10000610351562,
      "text": "Treat you",
      "start": 196.10000610351562
    }
  ],
